install this packages on Debian:

    python-sphinx
    texlive-xetex
    texlive-latex-recommended
    texlive-latex-extra
    lmodern

if you want livereload(https://github.com/mockko/livereload), install `python-pip`, and run:

    $ pip install livereload

to generate HTML:

    $ make html

to generate PDF:

    $ make latexpdf

to use livereload:

    $ make livehtml
